# Documentation language: English only

- All documentation must be written in **English**.
- This includes (non-exhaustive): `README*`, `CHANGELOG*`, `CONTRIBUTING*`, `SECURITY*`, `docs/**`, `**/*.md`, `**/*.mdx`, and any user-facing help text intended as documentation.
- If existing documentation is in another language, translate it to English rather than adding a new non-English section.
- Do not add bilingual/multilingual blocks (e.g., French + English). Keep a single English source of truth.

